SUMMARY:Meet the Greek and Roman Gods
DESCRIPTION:Examine figures and symbols while hearing tales of their adve
 ntures and exploits. Compare and contrast the deities that ancient artist
 s and worshippers adored over the centuries.  About Your Guide  This publ
 ic tour will be hosted by Dr. TammyJo Eckhart who is an ancient historian
  with scholarly work in the fields of folklore and popular culture. An aw
 ard-winning educator and author\, she looks forward to sharing knowledge 
 with you and seeing each god with renewed interest through your observati
 ons.  Know Before You GoSpace is available for the first 12 people to che
 ck in with Guest Services on the day. Drop by the information desk on the
  first floor of the museum when you arrive.A small handbag may be carried
  at your side. Backpacks and large bags will need to be stored before tou
 ring. Learn more aboutmuseum guidelines.If you park in the IMU parking lo
 t\, Guest Services can validate your parking voucher for a discount.Read 
 aboutwhere to find us and where to park\,
