X-LIVEWHALE-SUMMARY:<p>The Center for Theoretical Inquiry in the Humaniti
 es presents a symposium on Montaigne's <em>Essays</em>\, convened by Herb
 ert Marks (Comparative Literature) and Hall Bj├Ėrnstad (French and Italia
 n). Guest speakers Antonia Szabari (University of Southern California) an
 d Pierre Lyraud (University of Montreal) are joined by Alison Calhoun and
  Eric MacPhail (both IU Bloomington). We are grateful for support from th
 e Departments\, of Comparative Literature\, French &amp\; Italian\, and G
 ermanic Studies.</p>
