  she will share her deep passion for the arts and her expertise in the fi
 eld.  About Your Guide  Mindy N. Besaw\, Ph. D\, is the Wilma E. Kelley D
 irector of the IU Eskenazi Museum of Art and a scholar of American Art Hi
 story. As director\, Besaw oversees all facets of the museum's strategy\,
  operations\, and engagement\, including exhibitions\, collections\, teac
 hing partnerships\, and public programming. Read her bio. (https://artmus
 eum.indiana.edu/about/staff/_director/besaw-mindy.html)Know Before You Go
